{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you're liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, we'll take care of you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were other priests.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were-- there were reverends, you know, chaplains from the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they wanted to know who's a Catholic, who is a Protestant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, they-- for some of them, they only got there in time to give them their last rites, actually, because, you know, our systems were so far gone, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like a clock winding down, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was laying there and what I was thinking, I says, I'm-- I'm happy-- I'm liberated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not sure that I could say that I was happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I felt that I'm safe more than happy, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I knew that there's no Nazi can hurt me anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was the feeling that I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I had this terrible sight in front of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, that did not make me feel happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was thinking, did anybody else survive from my family?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was the first thing that I was thinking about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so I was just laying there, you know, saying, you know, that's it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't have to worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somebody will take care of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was the most important thing, that I didn't have to look out, you know, how to survive another minute, you see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So, you know, there was a lot of movement of big trucks coming up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I saw field kitchens being pulled up by the Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember this huge trailer coming up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I remember sides of beef hanging down, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I thought this was really something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I never saw so much food in a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
